#
# GUIDELINE:
#   type:
#     - Build: brazil change, new dependency, etc
#     - Chore: non-prod code change which is neither fix, feature nor refactor
#     - Docs: only documentation
#     - Feature: code change for a feature
#     - Fix: code change for a bug fix
#     - Performance: code change for improving performance
#     - Refactor: code change which is neither a fix nor a feature
#     - Test: add or modify tests
#   subject:
#     - use the imperative, present tense: "add" not "added" nor "adds"
#     - don't capitalize the first letter
#     - no dot (.) at the end
#   body(optional):
#     - motivation for the change
#   testing:
#     - testing required for this change
#   footer:
#     - link to JIRA ticket
#     - link to reference documentation
#
